Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:08.23,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Within that warm dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.26,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I sleep sweetly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:22.02,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,From then on, I thought everything would be fine even if I kept sleeping like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:23.81,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.72,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:34.77,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There are many people living in this world filled with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:37.70,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Many people?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:43.07,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,The day will also come when you open your eyes.{be awaken}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:53.00,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You'll definitely bring happiness to those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:56.80,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I can... make them happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:00:58.23,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:01.95,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Because, that's the reason you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.03,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,The great person who created me, said those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:12.99,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,If they're true, then it'll be a very very wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:22.05,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,So, I've been thinking; the day has arrived for me to open my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:26.38,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,If there's someone next to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:34.54,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I must first let that person be happy, and become part of their family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.40,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I made a vow to those words in my heart.
