Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:15.72,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The trading city situated on the northern-most islets of the Nostrum district; Ert'Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.46,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,There are people from various countries in this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:22.00,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,gathering goods from different parts of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:25.29,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, this city is called The World's Treasury.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:30.18,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the entire city is busy preparing for the Harvest Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:34.74,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This year's festival coincides with the Meteor Shower, which happens once every seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:40.18,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the number of tourists in the city is as high as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:47.95,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,On the other side of this buzzing city sits our Guild house, Oasis. {Though she says Clan, guild sounds better?}
