Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:11.55,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Nina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:16.06,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Did you stay up all night working again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:21.20,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the automatic dishwasher that I invented is almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.63,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:27.75,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, today is the meteor shower, which happens only once every seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:31.27,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Carina-san is looking forward to it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.52,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:48.49,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord2.999999\fs52.499997\an4\shad2.999999\c&H66C9E1&\3c&H065A7F&\pos(210,702)\4c&H033045&}The Jewel of Ert'Aria\NCarina Verritti
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:48.19,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Is Leicester still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.42,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.11,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.57,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just got up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:58.76,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I poked your sleeping face first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:02.73,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I pinched your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:10.79,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,The Leicester who woke up due to breathing difficulties is looking at me with a warm smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.74,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.42,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.75,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Your sleeping face is so dashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:23.53,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, to me, Carina-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.14,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:28.33,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:29.98,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.35,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.74,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:43.32,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What a sour yet sweet kiss.
