Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:47.42,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:50.91,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nina, have you greeted Leicester?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.63,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:58.25,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to be the first person to greet Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:01.16,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:06.60,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Look, this makes you the first person to hold my hand today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:13.92,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:14.84,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:15.62,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
