Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.09,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is still beating non-stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.31,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Carina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.60,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
