Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:42.00,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we'll have to prepare properly for tonight's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:44.97,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.00,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:52.69,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,A doll? The craftsmanship is really complex. {Or a doll}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:56.48,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,How was it made?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:04.94,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously Leicester, you're always so mesmerized when you see things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:08.52,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:11.17,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It's over at the town{city} square. It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.48,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the puppets are moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:14.77,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.91,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:31.95,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Carina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.63,Default,People,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Carina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.07,Default,People,0000,0000,0000,,The lady from the Verritti family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.17,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, how do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.01,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I see, the Leis boy is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.30,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are close as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:49.00,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester, thanks for the clock you fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:52.08,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. If you need any help, feel free to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.73,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough already. Come over, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.65,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:58.00,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks everyone.
