Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:16.60,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.53,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:33.67,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.18,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if they are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:38.00,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Automatic puppets, Automata?
