Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.96,Default,People,0000,0000,0000,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.96,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,And, using this lively atmosphere; Tango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:51.35,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,That's the cat we saw earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.14,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Say hi to everyone, Tango.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:00.35,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tango the white cat, at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.20,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,The cat spoke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.76,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, this is the first time I've seen a talking automaton.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:09.34,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,You have great sight, Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.61,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:18.61,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,For today's special guest, we're inviting the "Jewel of Ert'Aria", Carina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:19.56,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.99,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,The best puppeteer in the world, Agnes's street acrobatics...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.89,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,...will now reach the climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.88,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,Clap, clap, clap...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:30.85,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.50,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to your performance, Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.31,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.81,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come down to this, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:42.30,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Puppet dance fest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.26,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's sure getting into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.44,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:48.60,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!{added this -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.67,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.07,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.60,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't we do it slowly? {that's what she said... -nt}
