Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.93,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you two. You lit up the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:52.58,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to have the help of the legendary Carina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.23,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,No no, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.70,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,We also enjoyed ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.51,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Tango-san seems to be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:03.82,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,The more intricate the automaton, the more Ale it consumes. {Note: Eru is the energy source of this world, a better spelling? XD}{Research indicates it's called Ale. -nt}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:03.80,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,[Ale: The energy source of this world]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.16,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,But, I think he'll wake up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:11.60,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, we have quite the feast here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:15.97,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,This amount of food is normal for people like us from Print'brise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:19.94,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,My, Agnes-san is from Print'brise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:23.56,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm in the middle of a journey for personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.08,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to stay here temporarily before the Harvest Festival ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.54,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I have to find a place here to stay quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.62,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come to our Guild house, Oasis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.46,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,There are still some vacant rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.82,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:38.79,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.50,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Leicester?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.28,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Clan Master and since you've decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.93,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to object.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.56,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.90,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Carina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:50.87,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.78,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,You should join us for the meteor shower tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:56.36,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}so{\i0} looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.86,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:01.43,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Knights Templar's parade. {or Knights of the Temple, Temple's Knights; your call Holo. -nt}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:05.51,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Knights Templar... Followers of Rangubasu? {TLC; what the heck is rangubasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:06.29,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:14.04,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,They are escorting the hidden treasure, Artifact, which is going to be displayed at the Harvest Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.05,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Artifact...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.21,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,You can see clearly from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:24.53,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Look Carina-sama, she is so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.75,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really. She looks very majestic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:32.96,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,She's looking this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:35.43,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't staring at others considered rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.22,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Ritos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:45.91,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,I did, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.53,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,We can't pretend we didn't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:52.55,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she actually ate so many desserts on her own and said it's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.65,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm referring to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:54.92,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,The meteor shower, meteor shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:56.31,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.37,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that "I don't care" face...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.30,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:03.65,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's chase after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.85,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.14,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stand here doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:09.52,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ritos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:10.83,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:11.65,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.90,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a sexy pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.98,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:28.49,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, it's very slippery there. You must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.65,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:42.54,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.94,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back! Leicester!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.97,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are late, Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.81,Default-Alt,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Aunt Shelley...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:58.34,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary for other people if you hug me suddenly like this, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.56,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:04.30,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord2.999999\fs52.499997\an4\shad2.999999\c&H66C9E1&\3c&H065A7F&\4c&H033045&\pos(1204.499972,691.500023)}Capricious Mother\NShelley Maycraft
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:03.17,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So, it's fine if no one else is watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.79,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,She's actually Leicester's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:09.56,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,She's so young; it gave me a huge shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.51,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, why thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.42,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes-chan is also very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.59,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Hello nice to meet you!{split these -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.61,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?{split these -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.57,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,There's still some time before the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.88,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, actually there's someone I wanted to introduce to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:30.07,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Though I did tell her to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.89,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Is she not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.28,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, it must be her old habit kicking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.14,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Shelley-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.46,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:44.67,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,There's actually someone strolling back and forth outside the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:47.74,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,That's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.95,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, Chelsea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:51.72,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!{added this -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:58.90,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord2.999999\fs52.499997\an4\shad2.999999\c&H66C9E1&\3c&H065A7F&\4c&H033045&\pos(1208.999945,698.999977)}Knights Templar\NChelsea Arcot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.93,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chelsea Arcot from the Knights Templar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.35,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Oasis Clan House.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.18,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Carina Verritti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.40,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry to bother you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:11.78,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Chelsea has always had a horrible sense of direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.11,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:17.46,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't she the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.57,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you're my Mom's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.45,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.{added this -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.92,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,We've known each other for quite a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.37,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidences really do happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:35.30,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Since she doesn't come to Ert'Aria often, I asked her to join us for tonight's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:38.54,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,We're honored to have you. {We are very honoured}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:43.40,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a bit early, but, shall we head to the party location?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.75,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.63,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,That's Nina-chan for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:50.10,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.84,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where will the party be held?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:02.18,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:07.13,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to get my Dad to let us use the roof of the cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.00,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,It's the highest point in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:13.52,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to see the meteor shower clearly from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.48,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! That's the daughter of the Verritti family for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.32,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, isn't that Carina-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.70,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-sama, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.64,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:27.14,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,The meteor shower is so exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:27.95,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.81,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The acrobatic girl from earlier is with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.55,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I really enjoyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.64,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Look look, she's from the Knights Templar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.50,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.68,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard to be surrounded by so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:49.01,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm really honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.43,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:54.68,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That woman's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:56.74,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,The guy next to her is also very cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.80,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,They make such a great couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.36,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, how embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:04.31,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm filled with envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.12,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be deceived, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.60,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.00,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,What? He greeted me so naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.23,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:20.51,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,We overheard that everyone in the Oasis Clan House will be watching the meteor shower in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:23.05,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,So, my sister stalked you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.59,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You were the one who said I should follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:30.25,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you pretend you don't care?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.95,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,You girls are still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.43,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these funny people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:41.03,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,They are from Tortilla Co. in front of our Clan House.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.19,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,100)\bord2.999999\fs52.499997\an4\shad2.999999\c&H66C9E1&\3c&H065A7F&\4c&H033045&\pos(500.999986,705.000023)}Younger of the Tortilla sisters\NRitos Tortilla
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.19,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,100)\bord2.999999\fs52.499997\an4\shad2.999999\c&H66C9E1&\3c&H065A7F&\4c&H033045&\pos(1208.999945,705.000023)}Older of the Tortilla sisters\NSalsa Tortilla
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.36,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Salsa-san and Ritos-san. {I lol'd. -nt}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:46.46,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Putting aside my sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.53,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,to say that I'm funny... I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.59,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything funny either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.52,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.22,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,I've been ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:56.14,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:58.09,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is Agnes-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.20,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the best puppeteer in the wold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.07,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:03.67,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,You actually dare to claim you're the best in the world in front of my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.79,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,How presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.29,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Salsa is also a puppeteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.62,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.74,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go about advertising me with things you just made up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.80,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's caused trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.58,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:17.52,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Since when?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.23,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:23.64,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, she's Chelsea-san from the Knights Templar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:24.70,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:28.48,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,What were you two saying about not being deceived?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.23,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:34.33,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, don't be deceived!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:37.28,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,This person isn't Leicester's girlfriend, but his mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:41.16,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Right, it'll be bad if this doesn't get sorted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.22,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.05,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.36,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it means... {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.38,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:53.92,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,It means, I am the person whom Leicester-san is going to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.11,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,No, what do you mean by "marry"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:55.79,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.09,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you disregard me and go on talking about getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.99,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey that's not fair! I want to marry him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.41,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, what's with the marrying thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.68,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,OK then, just let him marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.47,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.42,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are popular, Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:15.40,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Milady, chatting may be a good thing but time is of the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.15,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.48,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:21.70,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Strange? I thought you guys were viewing the Meteor Shower from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.36,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:26.87,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,We are having a party on the roof of the cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:28.93,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:34.08,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to let the people worship you from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.50,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.04,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Would you two like to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:39.52,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:43.58,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the offer, but we are viewing it from an even higher place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:45.98,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:49.26,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go somewhere that's much, much higher than the cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.27,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Is there such a place in this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:55.07,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.60,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take our leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:05.85,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:07.15,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.85,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Here, grab on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:11.99,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.96,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,We've been Walking{walking?} the entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:23.06,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if these stairs continued endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.93,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:37.76,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,The city's view is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.27,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually quite beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.73,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,It has a "Welcome to Ert'Aria" sort of feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.20,Default,People,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.{I just found this "sugoi" here -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Quick, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:15.84,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Chelsea's skin is so soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:17.23,Default-Alt,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Shelley, it tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.73,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Shelley-sama, please don't get too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:21.73,Default,Shelley,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:24.65,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.06,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It's mysterious, don't you think?
